  "original_title": "\u0b87.\u0baa\u0bcb.\u0b9a. \u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bcd. \u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0b8a\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b87\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb7\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "E.P.C. Jaffna. Road workers strike today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sri Lanka Transport Board's Jaffna. The road workers have announced that they have decided to go on strike today (24) and it has been reported that due to the shutdown of the Jaffna road, the operations of the roads connected to it will also be affected.",
        "The Jaffna Road employees made a joint announcement at a media conference held yesterday (23) at Jaffna Central Bus Station.",
        "Yesterday (22nd) at 9 o'clock in the night, both the driver and the guard of the 57-route EPO bus from Jaffna to Colombo were attacked by the employees of the Kalkamuwa Road EPO road in Thaladagama area.",
        "It has also been requested that the police immediately arrest the employees involved in the attack and take legal action.",
        "If legal action is not taken today (24) the Sri Lankan Transport Board's Jaffna Road is planning to carry out trade union protests along with Northern Regional Roads in Jaffna. The road workers had made a joint announcement yesterday. (a)"
      ],
